  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:66" id="Psalm-119-66">Teach me good judgment and knowledge,<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>for I believe in your commandments.<br/></span>
  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:67" id="Psalm-119-67">Before I was afflicted, I went astray;<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>but now I observe your word.<br/></span>
