  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:74" id="Psalm-119-74">Those who fear you will see me and be glad,<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>because I have put my hope in your word.<br/></span>
  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:75" id="Psalm-119-75">Yahweh, I know that your judgments are righteous,<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>that in faithfulness you have afflicted me.<br/></span>
