  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:77" id="Psalm-119-77">Let your tender mercies come to me, that I may live;<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>for your law is my delight.<br/></span>
  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:78" id="Psalm-119-78">Let the proud be disappointed, for they have overthrown me wrongfully.<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>I will meditate on your precepts.<br/></span>
