  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:80" id="Psalm-119-80">Let my heart be blameless toward your decrees,<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>that I may not be disappointed.<br/>   <br/>   KAF<br/>   <br/></span>
