  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:82" id="Psalm-119-82">My eyes fail for your word.<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>I say, &#8220;When will you comfort me?&#8221;<br/></span>
  <span class="verse" title="Psalm 119:83" id="Psalm-119-83">For I have become like a wineskin in the smoke.<br/> <span class="indent">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>I don&#8217;t forget your statutes.<br/></span>
